    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">This kit includes all of the necessary implements to prepare and create mundane weapons while in the presence or access of extreme heat and cooling capabilities.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Proficiency with this kit lets you add your proficiency bonus to any skill checks you make to make weapons.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Also, proficiency with this kit is required to create Chakra Enhanced Weapons of any type.</span></p><p> </p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Swift Craft DC: 24.</span></p>",
